OL,3,CFormer team mate holds fitness
OL,4,Cfundraiser for family of Joe Thompson
OL,6,FA friend and former teammate of the
OL,7,Flate Rochdale footballerJoe Thompson
OL,8,Fis holding a non-stop fitness session
OL,9,Fto raise money for Joe's family.
OL,11,FSimon Ramsden played at Rochdale FC
OL,12,Fwith Joe for six years. He is taking
OL,13,Fon the massive challenge of a 37 hour
OL,14,Fnon stop fitness session, accompanied
OL,15,Fby friends and former colleagues.
OL,17,FHe said: "One of Joe's sayings in life
OL,18,Fis "don't live life to survive, live
OL,19,Flife to thrive' and I think that's
OL,20,Fabsolutely right.
