OL,3,CFormer team mate holds fitness
OL,4,Cfundraiser for family of Joe Thompson
OL,6,F"I'm doing 37 hours, and seven rhymes
OL,7,Fwith heaven, so I could have taken the
OL,8,Feasy option and done 27 or a lesser
OL,9,Fnumber, but Joe never did anything by
OL,10,Fhalf, so I don't think I should
OL,11,Feither."
OL,13,FThompson - who battled cancer on three
OL,14,Foccasions - died at the age of 36 in
OL,15,FApril 2025.
OL,17,FHe played more than 200 games for
OL,18,FRochdale, and was first diagnosed with
OL,19,FHodgkin lymphoma in 2013 while playing
OL,20,Ffor Tranmere.
