OL,6,FHe later signed for Bury and spent
OL,7,Ftime on loan at Southport and Wrexham
OL,8,Fas he tried to build his match fitness
OL,9,Ffollowing treatment.
OL,11,FHe returned to Rochdale from Carlisle
OL,12,Fin 2016 but the disease soon returned,
OL,13,Frequiring extensive treatment.
OL,15,FThompson announced he was cancer free
OL,16,Fin June 2017 and less than a year
OL,17,Flater scored the goal that kept
OL,18,FRochdale in League One, beating
OL,19,FCharlton on the final day of the
OL,20,Fseason.
