OL,6,FHowever, he announced his retirement
OL,7,Ftwo years later, saying at the time
OL,8,Fhis body had been pushed "to the
OL,9,Flimit" by his two fights against
OL,10,FHodgkin lymphoma.
OL,12,FHe started his career in the
OL,13,FManchester United academy as a
OL,14,Fforward, and later returned to the
OL,15,Fclub as an Ambassador.
