OL,4,Cfundraiser for family of Joe Thompson
OL,6,FAfter he'd called time on his playing
OL,7,Fcareer, Joe took to fundraising and
OL,8,Fraising awareness of blood cancers,
OL,9,Fmost recently completing a 21-mile
OL,10,Fwalk from Old Trafford to Rochdale's
OL,11,FCrown Oil Arena.
OL,13,FSimon's challenge will raise money so
OL,14,Fthat Joe's wife Chantelle can take
OL,15,Ftheir daughters Lula and Athena Rae on
OL,16,Fa dream holiday to New York, something
OL,17,Fthat Joe had promised 12 year-old Lula.
