OL,6,FHe said: "The donations are coming in
OL,7,Fleft, right and centre from all over
OL,8,Fthe country. It's been a crazy few
OL,9,Fhours with no sleep and we will be
OL,10,Ftraining through the night, but its
OL,11,Fall for an amazing cause."
OL,13,F"Joe was an amazing man and a great
OL,14,Ffriend to me - we want to be able to
OL,15,Fgive something back to his kids. Every
OL,16,Fpenny will go to them."
